  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient with angor, patients with only one de novo lesion. Target zone must be &lt; 52
             mm, artery section must be &lt; 3,7mm and &gt; 2,25 mm

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Vessel with extremely tortuous proximal segment, lesion with angulous segments (&gt;90°)
             Unstable ventricular arrhythmia, dialysis, MI within the last 72 hours etc…
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
